    <title type="html">指南</title>
    <id>https://vuepress-theme-hope.gitee.io/v1/copy-code/zh/guide.html</id>
    <link href="https://vuepress-theme-hope.gitee.io/v1/copy-code/zh/guide.html"/>
    <updated>2022-06-03T13:41:37.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用"> 使用</h2>
<p>此插件会自动添加复制按钮到每个代码块的右下角。</p>
<p>默认情况下，按钮仅在桌面模式显示，如果你需要在移动端展示这个按钮，请将 <code>showInMobile</code> 设置为 <code>true</code>。</p>
<p>在用户点击复制按钮后，屏幕上会显示一个复制成功的提示。默认的提示时长为 2000ms，如果你需要更改这个时长，请设置 <code>duration</code>(单位 ms)，如果你不需要这个提示，请将 <code>duration</code> 设置为 <code>0</code>。</p>
<h2 id="演示"> 演示</h2>
<CodeGroup>
<CodeGroupItem title=" TS">
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.ts</span>
<span>export</span> <span>default</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"copy-code1"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 插件选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
<CodeGroupItem title=" JS">
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  <span>plugins</span><span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"copy-code1"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 插件选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
</CodeGroup>
]]></content>
